# Edward Siarka

Edward Siarka (born 7 July 1963 in Rabka) is a Polish politician. He was elected to the Sejm on 25 September 2005, getting 10,778 votes in 14 Nowy SÄ…cz district as a candidate from the Law and Justice list.
He was re-elected on 10 October 2019.
